00:23:38,631 --> 00:23:39,010
Scott: SNES.

422
00:23:39,650 --> 00:23:43,190
Rym: You gotta be a little more evil here if you want to really make money.

423
00:23:43,410 --> 00:23:43,978
Scott: No, no, no.

424
00:23:44,119 --> 00:23:44,849
Scott: I'm not done yet.

425
00:23:45,451 --> 00:23:47,640
