00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:48,021
Scott: Big time.

427
00:23:50,870 --> 00:23:53,266
Scott: Everyone's like, "Oh shit, people are lining up to buy that

428
00:23:53,307 --> 00:23:53,770
Scott: motherfucker.".

