430
00:23:56,310 --> 00:24:11,570
Scott: And then, right, what you do is you still charge in the DSiWare, the downloadable area, you know, the DSware, you know, sort of the WiiWare equivalent indie games, and you gotta allow the indie games in, obviously.

431
00:24:11,850 --> 00:24:12,870
Scott: We've talked about that in the past.

432
00:24:13,151 --> 00:24:14,189
